ething is made with care, it isn’t just packaging—it’s Kind of April. 🌸<\/p>","button_label":"Explore Our Products","button_link":""}},"image_banner_ftEb6L":{"type":"image-banner","blocks":{"heading_VpNpin":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"","heading_size":"h1"}},"text_W9bzKp":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"","text_style":"body"}},"buttons_jbHe3P":{"type":"buttons","settings":{"button_label_1":"","button_link_1":"","button_style_secondary_1":false,"button_label_2":"","button_link_2":"","button_style_secondary_2":false}}},"block_order":["heading_VpNpin","text_W9bzKp","buttons_jbHe3P"],"name":"t:sections.image-banner.presets.name","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Frame_440.png","image_overlay_opacity":0,"image_height":"medium","image_behavior":"none","desktop_content_position":"middle-center","desktop_content_alignment":"center","show_text_box":false,"color_scheme":"","stack_images_on_mobile":false,"mobile_content_alignment":"center","show_text_below":false}},"custom_carousel_jejtAF":{"type":"custom-carousel","blocks":{"testimonial_KtjkdQ":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Blended_co.heic","logo":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Blended_co.png","testimonial":"<p>Kind of April has been our go-to for standout potli packaging. They’re responsive, detail-driven, and consistently deliver top-notch quality. KOA isn’t just a vendor—they’re a dependable partner who genuinely cares about our vision.<\/p>","author_name":"Sanya Aggarwal","author_title":"Partner, The Blended Co."}},"testimonial_Kicbpt":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Las_maracus.heic","logo":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Las_Ma.png","testimonial":"<p>Working with KOA PACK was a smooth and seamless experience. They were prompt, responsive, and detail-oriented throughout the process. The quality of the tote bags was exactly what we hoped for—well-crafted and thoughtfully executed. Really appreciated how easy they were to coordinate 